Pre-Game Insights: Desiree Ellis likened their 2024 Olympic qualifier against Nigeria to the final round in a boxing match where a boxer has to deliver a knockout to win.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The second leg will be played at Loftus Stadium on April 9 and tickets for that game went on sale last week.
Others: Refiloe Jane and defenders Bambanani Mbane, Sibulele Holweni, and Bongeka Gamede from injuries will return to the team.
